the swan princess : princess tomorrow , pirate today is a 2016 american computer-animated family/fantasy film produced by crest animation productions , nest family entertainment and streetlight productions , directed by richard rich and starring the voices of jayden isabel as alise and grant durazzo as lucas . it is the sixth film in the swan princess series , and follows the adventures of odette and derek 's daughter alise on her first journey as a member of the royal family overseas . it was released direct-to-dvd and blu-ray on september 6 , 2016 . a seventh film released in 2017 and an eighth film is in production .